mpaign impressively when in the placings over 2200m at Jagersro. Now under the care of new trainer A Massaad. Looks a winning chance. 3. AQUAMAN resumes after a break of 11 months. Did win at his only other first-up run when on debut, scoring over 1850m at Cologne. One of the genuine hopes in the race. 5. LIFETIMES was well held in the Prix Hocquart won by Rafale Design over 2200m at Longchamp at his last appearance 11 months ago. Should camp just off the leaders. Sure to be competitive. 6. SEDANO is back at the races for the first time since July 6. Worth noting he filled a minor placing when returning from a spell last time in work over 2000m at Strasbourg. Can make his presence felt.\",\"runners\":[4,3,5,6],\"exclusive\":false}","tips":{"tipType":"Standard","tipster":"Wett Star Germany","tipRunnerNumbers":[5,6,3]},"ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[4,5,3,6]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[4,3,6,1]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,4,6,2]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[6,4,1,3]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,1,5,3]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[4,3,6,1]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[4,1,6,3]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"DDF","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"DDF","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"DDF","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"DDF","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"DDF","raceType":"R"}}]}}}